artwork.name: 27 Heaven - Made it to 28
artwork.description:
i made it to 28 on 07/27/2021. All praise to the most high.

My NFT collaboration with No.1 NY Times bestselling author, musician and award winning film director Ian Halperin. This piece pays tribute to the club of artists who died at age 27, while celebrating life for all that are still here. Ian's original music depicts a haunting, yet inspiring feel, immortalizing the 27 club onto the blockchain.

The first collector of this token will unlock the one and only copy of Halperin's new book â€“ 27 Heaven. Only one edition of the book will ever be printed, as Ian's genesis piece dropped on my 28th birthday. Rest in peace to all those who have left us inspired.
